snippet.title: Racket Club - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase Winter 2023
snippet.description: Racket Club will be available on Meta Quest, Pico, and SteamVR on December 14, 2023. Watch the latest trailer for Racket Club to see gameplay, along with some of the features of this VR racket sport game, including the single-player career mode and more. Racket Club takes all the fun of tennis and pickleball to create a brand new racket sport, built from the ground up for VR.
